

'''iKarma'''

URL = http://ikarma.com/ 


=Description=

ikarma, which is a webservice that allows you to build reputation through ratings and reviews by clients, peers, collegues,... The idea behind it is that you copy the "ikarma seal" in your e-mail signatures, your website or blog, or even in your printed communication. The seal leads to your iKarma page, upon which people can read what other people think about you.
